snippet.title: Mangle Reveal FNAF AR: Special Delivery
snippet.description:
Now it's my turn to play take-apart-and-put-back-together...

Mangle has officially joined Five Nights at Freddy's AR: Special Delivery. If you haven't already, you can download the game on both iOS and Android.
🎮 Play FNAF AR: http://onelink.to/2em4am
🐻📦 FNAF AR Merch: http://merch.fnafar.com
